{"id":"6405","user":{"id":"214296","nickname":"主播喵副本","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FmnbCWV2OzmsQSOnJc8r6Tte5W25","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【萌新院】添加本地磁盘教程","content":"<p>大家好，好久不见，我现在不止教mod了哦，今天我要教的是，如何添加本地磁盘。</p>\n<p>我们打开电脑（废话）</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgWGChd0-6UDzxUZw9tfCHP3fxW1\"><br></p>\n<p>看见那个计算机了吧，win5的同志叫“我的电脑”</p>\n<p>我们右键单击，会发现，有一个管理的按钮，我们左键单击它。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FrTexuqkOzFLtcS6odBtHoEcR4CM\"><br></p>\n<p>嗯好，你点击以后，会发现里面有这样一幅长眠。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgAdi350epg3m27RTovMrwfzGgas\"><br></p>\n<p>左键双击“储存”，然后左键双击“磁盘管理（本地）”会有这样的场面</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FnMTygSQ5YA1XmQn0Nob5Dae2dzY\"><br></p>\n<p>右键单击较大的一块区域，选择压缩卷。</p>\n<p>一小时后······</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FoUZpRG2M4G0VGDINxFAagkcP6GJ\"><br></p>\n<p>抱歉我家的电脑网速有点慢。</p>\n<p>又过了一小时</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FoUZpRG2M4G0VGDINxFAagkcP6GJ\"><br></p>\n<p>好了，你发现压缩完之后会有一快区域</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fnui0SRpcR7wSQ9a7rvrwAwXcB76\"><br></p>\n<p>请右键单击它，选中新建简单卷，一直点击下一步就好了，你会发现你有了一个新磁盘，给它改名叫做“本地磁盘吧！</p>","board_id":"2","board_name":"积木编程乐园","updated_at":1505575811,"created_at":1505308783,"n_views":182,"n_replies":13,"n_comments":0,"is_authorized":false,"is_featured":false,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinned":false,"tutorial_flag":0,"ask_help_flag":0}